    SocketGroup >= 4BBBR 4GGBR 4BBBB 4GG 4RR
    AreaLevel < 81
    BaseArmour > 1
    Continue
  Show
    BaseType "Body Armours"
    Rarity Rare
    SocketGroup >= 4BBBR 4GGBR 4BBBB 4GG 4RR
    AreaLevel < 81
    BaseArmour > 1
    BaseEnergyShield > 1
    LinkedSockets >= 4


